INTRODUCTION

This plugin will enable an input element to receive numeric input and output words equivalent into an element.
Currently, by default will postpend DOLLARS and CENTS accordingly. Internationalization is supported through
plugin options during initialization. Please see the demo.html on usage example.

Please send comments and feature request through "Issues" in github.

Thank you.

